2001-09-11 Michael Reinelt <reinelt@eunet.at>
use new extended tokens to split up several data sources
(CPU, Net, Disk, ISDN, ...)
e.g. '%nw'  is 'network transmit' for _all_ devices
     '%n0w' is 'network transmit' for eth0
     '%n1w' for eth1

